						</div>
						<div class="panel-body">
							<p>WebRTC is an API definition being drafted by the World Wide Web Consortium to enable browser-to-browser applications for voice calling, video chat, and P2P file sharing without plugins. Its mission is to enable rich, high quality, RTC applications to be developed in the browser via simple JavaScript APIs and HTML5. For more information, visit the <a href="http://www.webrtc.org/">offical WebRTC website</a>.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

