						<div class="panel-heading">
							<h3 class="panel-title">Can bitflop games be monitored or recorded?</h3>
						</div>
						<div class="panel-body">
							<p>Bitflop is designed to run voice and video peer-to-peer directly between calling parties, which is encrypted and does not pass through our servers. That means any video and/or audio cannot be monitored or recorded. Game data however, is exchanged with our servers while the game is in play. This data is also encrypted to prevent any eavesdropping or monitoring.</p>
